course: main course
time required: 10m
---

Wash and dry produce.

Halve, core, and thinly slice @apple{1}. Cut @prosciutto{2%ounce} into strips
lengthwise, then halve crosswise.

In a #large bowl{}, combine @arugula{2%ounce}, apple, prosciutto, half the
@feta cheese{1/2%cup}, a large drizzle of @olive oil{2%teaspoon}, @salt{1%teaspoon},
and @black pepper{1%teaspoon}.

Divide salad between #bowls{}.

Garnish with @pecans{1/2%ounce} and remaining feta. Drizzle with as much
@balsamic glaze{5%teaspoon} as you like and serve.

> A crisp, refreshing salad that hits all the notes—peppery arugula, juicy
> apple, salty prosciutto, and tangy feta. Pecans bring the crunch, while a
> drizzle of balsamic glaze adds a sweet-tangy finish that makes every bite pop!